{"tid":1557624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港隊需要大家支持","createTime":"2019-09-10T07:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:01:52.000Z","uid":48659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db5880d7b8f13e80f33b7059296e3eeda1026561","tid":1557624,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:48:05.000Z","msg":"香港隊呢幾十年黎係弱旅<br />\n但間唔中都踢出左唔少既爭氣波比香港人睇<br />\n好似兩和中國及巴林 又係上年既東亞盃外圍賽壓過北韓出線等<br />\n但係香港足球咁既資源同硬件配套發展下真係唔算失禮架啦  足球發展同青訓一樣都係要球迷支持<br />\n但試想香港人又有幾常會入場睇波啊<br />\n希望大家唔好只係今次入場支持就算<br />\n足球發展係需要持續支持 唔係一朝一夕既事黎<br />\n大家以後都多啲入場支持香港隊同本地球會 <br />\n發展好我地既本地足球啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個本地足球fans 上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcddfa505eb601f1e4c4935ccf6c2d31fdafb33","tid":1557624,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258c41c0b6a41be5c3815c3b36f9c74efeb7a566","tid":1557624,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"c161bc7ecf566f32a6208d4e4cab7e00ade6303b","tid":1557624,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ff711b85537a1973f6c18edfe0884729cfbf456","tid":1557624,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}